content:
{
  "plan": "Initiative order determined for Round 1: Shadow of Sir Garran (17), then Norn (16). Shadow of Sir Garran to act first, followed by Norn's turn. Monitor HP and status for both combatants. Await player action after initial enemy attack.",
  "narration": "The air in Sir Garran Vael's private study thickens with an eerie chill as a shadowy form coalesces near the arcane containment circle. This spectral figure, the Shadow of Sir Garran, the cursed guardian of the sanctum, fixes its glowing, cruel eyes on you. Its translucent blade pulses with malevolent energy, ready to strike with the fury of a fallen knight bound to dark forces. The whispering shadows seem to flicker and dance around the room's wood-paneled walls, as the ancient grandfather clock ticks backwards ominously. Standing amidst the scattered parchments and arcane symbols, you steel yourself for the coming duel. The Shadow of Sir Garran moves first, its swift, unnatural grace making clear this will be a deadly fight.\n\nYour current health is 12 out of 47 hit points, and your armor gleams dully in the dim light. The spectral enemy shadows your every move. The initiative order holds: the Shadow will act first, then you. Prepare yourself, Norn. What will be your first move in this deadly contest?",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Shadow of Sir Garran makes two attacks with disadvantage against Norn's AC 19. Use prerolled attack rolls 17/9 for first attack (lower 9 + 8 = 17 vs AC 19, miss) and 7/11 for second attack (lower 7 + 7 =14 vs AC 19, miss). Both attacks miss. No damage applied. Await player turn to act. Combat round remains 1.",
  "narration": "The Shadow of Sir Garran glides forward, its ghostly blade cutting through the air toward you. Protected by your ward's favor and resilient armor, you watch intently as it strikes with deadly intent. For its first attack, the shadow swings its Shadow Blade, but the swing falls short as you deftly parry with your shield. The attack rolls against you showed promise but ultimately missed, your armor deflecting its spectral energy.\n\nNot deterred, the shadow lashes out with its chilling touch, a cold hand reaching to freeze your very soul. Yet again, your ward shields you as the ghostly grasp slips through your defenses, missing its mark.\n\nBoth foes’ attacks falter before your steadfast defense. The shadow recoils momentarily, eyes flickering with frustration. Now, Norn, the moment is yours. What will you do next in this chilling battle?",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Norn performs two attacks with longsword using improved critical (crit on 19-20). Roll damage twice for each attack due to crit. Await player's roll results for damage dice.",
  "narration": "You tighten your grip on your longsword, muscles tensing as you launch into your assault on the Shadow of Sir Garran. Your first attack flies true as you roll a 19, triggering your improved critical strike. You follow with a second strike, your blade flashing and striking with deadly precision on a natural 20. Both hits pierce the ethereal form, slicing into the shadowy essence with brutal force. Please roll your damage dice twice per attack for critical hits, and tell me the total damage dealt from both strikes.",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Apply Norn's total damage of 18 and 17 respectively to Shadow of Sir Garran's HP, reducing it from 90 to 55. Apply the damage as slashing. Norn uses Second Wind to heal 1d10+5 HP. Use next d10 roll (1) plus 5 for 6 HP healed, increasing HP from 12 to 18. Update their HP accordingly.",
  "narration": "Your longsword bites deep twice into the Shadow of Sir Garran's ephemeral form, the first strike carving through the darkness with a fierce slash dealing 18 damage, the second following swiftly, cleaving another 17 points of life from the shadowy knight. It recoils, the malevolent glow in its eyes dimming momentarily as it writhes, but it remains a deadly adversary.\n\nFeeling the strain of battle, you invoke your fighter's resilience with a quick intake of breath and a fierce grit to fuel your Second Wind, mending your wounds. You regain 6 hit points, bolstering your strength to continue the fight with renewed vitality.\n\nThe Shadow clutches at its wound, shadows swirling violently as we prepare for the next move. What will you do now, Norn?",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "C07-E1",
        "changes": "Shadow of Sir Garran takes 35 slashing damage from Norn's longsword attacks, HP reduced from 90 to 55."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "updateCharacterInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "characterName": "Norn",
        "changes": "Regains 6 hit points from Second Wind, HP increased from 12 to 18."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "plan": "Await player's attack roll inputs to proceed with attack actions this turn. Norn can perform two attacks due to Extra Attack feature.",
  "narration": "The Shadow struggles with the searing pain of your strikes, but the battle is far from over. Now is your opportunity to press the advantage. Ready your weapon and strike swiftly. Please roll your attack rolls for your two attacks, adding your attack bonus of +5 to each. Remember, you have improved critical on 19 or 20.",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Current combat round is 1. It is Norn's turn to act after Shadow of Sir Garran completed its attacks.",
  "narration": "The first round of combat is underway. The Shadow of Sir Garran has just finished its attacks and now it's your turn, Norn. Your health stands at 18 out of 47 hit points, while the shadowy foe has taken a serious blow, carrying 55 out of its original 90 hit points remaining. You feel the weight of the fight pressing in, but your resolve is strong. What will you do next in this tense battle?",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Apply Norn's attack damage of 18 and 19 to Shadow of Sir Garran, reducing its HP from 55 to 18. Await next creature's turn. Combat round remains 1 until Shadow of Sir Garran acts.",
  "narration": "Channeling your fighter's focus, you strike the Shadow of Sir Garran twice more with deadly precision. The first blow connects solidly, tearing 18 points of slashing energy from the spectral foe, causing it to stagger under the assault. Your second strike follows immediately—a critical hit, slicing through the shadow's form and dealing 19 damage. The shadow reels, its essence flickering as it stands on the verge of collapse but still threatens.\n\nThe room is heavy with tension as the Shadow gathers itself for its counterattack. Brace yourself, Norn—the battle rages on.",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "C07-E1",
        "changes": "Shadow of Sir Garran takes 37 slashing damage from Norn's longsword attacks, HP reduced from 55 to 18."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "plan": "Shadow of Sir Garran takes its turn now with two attacks: Shadow Blade hit with d20 roll 9 + 8 =17 vs AC 19 (miss), Chilling Touch hit with d20 roll 18 + 7 = 25 vs AC 19 (hit). Chilling Touch damage roll d6 3 + 2 =5 cold damage to Norn. After Shadow's turn, round 1 is complete, advancing combat_round to 2. Next is Norn's turn.",
  "narration": "Wounded but relentless, the Shadow of Sir Garran swings its spectral blade with deadly intent, but your armor absorbs the blow, and the attack fails to connect.\n\nUndeterred, it reaches out with a chilling touch, its icy fingers lashing against you. The cold bites deep, and you feel the fragile warmth within diminish as frost creeps over your skin, dealing 5 points of cold damage.\n\nThe first round of combat closes with the air heavy and charged for what is to come. Now, the second round begins, Norn. The shadow looms, but your resolve hardens. What will you do next?",
  "combat_round": 2,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateCharacterInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "characterName": "Norn",
        "changes": "Takes 5 cold damage from Shadow of Sir Garran's chilling touch, HP reduced from 18 to 13."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "plan": "Apply Norn's total 19 damage to Shadow of Sir Garran, reducing its HP from 18 to -1, resulting in death. Update Shadow's status to dead. Initiate end of combat sequence with exit action after updates.",
  "narration": "With fierce determination, you launch a final series of strikes against the Shadow of Sir Garran. Your first attack lands solidly, tearing through the wraithlike form and dealing 9 points of damage. The second blow strikes true as well, carving away another 10 points. The shadow staggers, flickers, then dissipates in a swirl of darkness, its menace finally ended.\n\nThe silence that follows is almost deafening as the spectral guardian fades into the shadows it once commanded. Victory is yours, Norn. The lord's study, once haunted by shadow and sorrow, feels lighter, as if releasing a long-held breath.\n\nWhat will you do next now that the threat has been vanquished?",
  "combat_round": 2,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "C07-E1",
        "changes": "Shadow of Sir Garran takes 19 slashing damage from Norn's longsword attacks, HP reduced from 18 to -1. Status changed to dead."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "exit",
      "parameters": {}
    }
  ]
}

Combat Summary: {
  "narration": "In the shadowed private study of Sir Garran Vael, Norn faced the fearsome Shadow of Sir Garran, a spectral guardian wielding a malevolent blade. The battle began with the ghostly knight attacking, but Norn's wards and armor thwarted each deadly strike. Seizing the opportunity, Norn unleashed a devastating counterattack, scoring multiple critical hits and inflicting heavy damage. Despite the shadow's relentless assaults, including a chilling touch that dealt cold damage to Norn, the fighter's resilience and precise strikes wore down the foe. In the second round, Norn's focused attacks culminated in the Shadow's dissolution, ending the spectral threat and restoring a fragile calm to the arcane-laden chamber. With the Shadow of Sir Garran defeated, Norn earned 2900 experience points for the victory.",
  "combat_round": 2,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "LordStudyCombat",
        "changes": "Shadow of Sir Garran takes 72 damage, HP reduced from 90 to 18 after first round; further 19 damage in second round reduces HP from 18 to 0, Shadow defeated and dissipated."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "updateCharacterInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "characterName": "Norn",
        "changes": "HP reduced from 18 to 13 due to 5 cold damage from Shadow's chilling touch; healed earlier with Second Wind to 18 HP; status alive, condition none."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "exit"
    }
  ]
}
